<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN300-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai – tumpai; tuṟai – tāṉaimaṟam. aricilkiḻār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN300">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>tōṟā tōṟā veṉṟi tōloṭu</l>
<l>tuṟukaṉ maṟaiyiṉu muykuvai pōlāy</l>
<l>nerunal lellainī yeṟintōṉ ṟampi</l>
<l>yakalpey kuṉṟiyiṟ cuḻaluṅ kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>pērū raṭṭa kaḷḷiṟ</l>
<l>kōriṟ kōyiṟ ṟērumā ṉiṉṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>You may [well] say “shield [me], shield [me]!” Even if you hide</l>
<l>with the shield behind a thick stone, it seems you will not escape.</l>
<l>The younger brother of the one you slayed yesterday [now], </l>
<l>his eyes rolling like Kuṉṟi seeds poured into a bowl,</l>
<l>he will for sure [have to] search you like the ladle in the single house</l>
<l>for toddy which is prepared in the great village.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
